source.name: Campaign Finance Filers on Record with the New York State Board of Elections
source.description: This dataset contains information on the candidates and/or committees who file campaign finance disclosure information with the NYS Board of Elections. This data covers the period from July of 1999 through April 15th, 2013. For updated information, please visit http://www.elections.ny.gov
